"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"language":"diu","lang_name":"Rugciriku"},{"language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"language":"se","lang_name":"Sami"},{"language":"shs","lang_name":"Shuswap (Secwepemctsín)"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"sw","lang_name":"Swahili"},{"language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"language":"tl","lang_name":"Tagalog"},{"language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"language":"th","lang_name":"Thai"},{"language":"thp","lang_name":"Thompson"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"language":"ur","lang_name":"Urdu"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"fy","lang_name":"Western Frisian"}]},{"phelps":"TMP00662","text":"## A NIARING URE RA VINIVEL\n\nA vinevel na bura tara gai Kai Ala (Lolovina) tara  vavaurua nabung tuk tara uravinun na bung kai ra  vavautuea gai. Togono ra umana bung koko da ian ta  magit ma koko da momo na tava livuan tara pakana  bung a matana keake I tutua ma I ki ba. lara  pakanabung upi da araring ma vagomgom ra tulungean  tabu. Gono ra vinevel vakir I ot pa nina diat a vinun ma  ailima kadia kilala, aumana tena vinavana aumana mait  ma lapun ma a vavina Ibalaure ra nat na bul ba I varvau  boko. \n\nA ngatngat na Luluai I Ari iau vevel tara umana magit na palapaka, ma vakir iau ian ma momo, dari una vagomgom ma dalu ra buai gu ma kaum varmari na varvalaun, ma bula vabakite iau ma balaure ra tulungeagu tara umana varvakaina kai ra ebar na tabaran, pi a tulungeagu na kiguvai mara vuvu gomgom ma vevel tara umana magit ma ki maravai piram","name":"A NIARING URE RA VINIVEL"}]
